OL,5, A lifelong friend of the Queen has     
OL,6, described Netflix's royal drama The    
OL,7, Crown as "complete fantasy" and "so    
OL,8, unfair on members of the Royal Family".
OL,10,FLady Glenconner, who was a maid of     
OL,11,Fhonour at the Queen's coronation, said 
OL,12,Fthe show "just makes me so angry".     
OL,14,F"The trouble is that people, especially
OL,15,Fin America, believe it completely," she
OL,16,Ftold BBC Radio 4's Woman's Hour.       
OL,18,FNetflix has defended the show, saying  
OL,19,Fit "has always been presented as a     
OL,20,Fdrama based on historical events".     
